---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import CTA from '../components/CTA.astro';
import HeroSection from '../components/HeroSection.jsx';
---

<Layout title="Quick2query - Our Journey">
  <Header />
  <main>
    <HeroSection 
      title="Our"
      highlight="Journey"
      subtitle="Discover how Quick2query emerged from the complexities of data analysis, and how we're revolutionizing the way businesses interact with their data through natural language."
      client:load
    />

    <!-- Story Content -->
    <section class="py-16">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-text font-primary">From Data Complexity to Conversational Simplicity</h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 font-secondary">
              Every breakthrough begins with a challenge that demands an innovative solution.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-16">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-text font-primary">The Challenge</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 font-secondary">
                In today's data-driven world, businesses were struggling with a critical bottleneck: 
                the gap between business users who understand their data needs and technical teams 
                who can write complex SQL queries to extract insights.
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 font-secondary">
                This disconnect was causing delays, inefficiencies, and missed opportunities across industries.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-background/30 border-2 border-tech/20 rounded-xl p-8">
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <div class="flex items-center">
                  <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-tech rounded-full mr-3"></div>
                  <span class="text-tech font-medium">73% of business users dependent on IT for data queries</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center">
                  <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-tech rounded-full mr-3"></div>
                  <span class="text-tech font-medium">Average 48-hour delay for data request fulfillment</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center">
                  <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-tech rounded-full mr-3"></div>
                  <span class="text-tech font-medium">85% of time spent on query writing vs. analysis</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center">
                  <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-tech rounded-full mr-3"></div>
                  <span class="text-tech font-medium">Limited access to data insights</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-16">
            <div class="bg-primary/10 border-2 border-primary/20 rounded-xl p-8">
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <div class="flex items-center">
                  <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-primary rounded-full mr-3"></div>
                  <span class="text-primary font-medium">Advanced Natural Language Processing</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center">
                  <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-primary rounded-full mr-3"></div>
                  <span class="text-primary font-medium">Context-Aware Query Generation</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center">
                  <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-primary rounded-full mr-3"></div>
                  <span class="text-primary font-medium">Multi-Database Support</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center">
                  <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-primary rounded-full mr-3"></div>
                  <span class="text-primary font-medium">Enterprise-Grade Security</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-text font-primary">The Innovation</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 font-secondary">
                Our team of AI experts, data scientists, and industry veterans came together to create 
                Quick2query. We developed a sophisticated natural language processing system that bridges 
                the gap between human thinking and database queries.
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 font-secondary">
                Our API doesn't just translate text to SQL â€“ it understands business context, optimizes queries, 
                and ensures data security at every step.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6 text-text font-primary">The Impact</h3>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
              <div class="bg-primary/10 border-2 border-primary/20 rounded-xl p-6">
                <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-2 font-primary">95%</div>
                <div class="text-primary font-medium font-secondary">Query Accuracy Rate</div>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-tech/10 border-2 border-tech/20 rounded-xl p-6">
                <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-tech mb-2 font-primary">500K+</div>
                <div class="text-tech font-medium font-secondary">Queries Processed Daily</div>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-accent/10 border-2 border-accent/20 rounded-xl p-6">
                <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent mb-2 font-primary">85%</div>
                <div class="text-accent font-medium font-secondary">Time Saved on Data Analysis</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-neutral rounded-xl p-8 text-center">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-text font-primary">Our Vision</h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto font-secondary">
              To democratize data access by making database interactions as natural as human conversation, 
              enabling businesses to unlock the full potential of their data through the power of AI and 
              natural language processing.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <CTA />
  <Footer />
</Layout>